fc: class Solution { private:     int m, n; public:     void solve(vector<vector<char>>& board) {         if(board.size() == 0) return ;         m = board.size(), n = board[0].size();         for(int i = 0; i < m; i++) {             dfs(i, 0, board);             dfs(i, n - 1, board);         }         for(int j = 0; j < n; j++) {             dfs(0, j, board);             dfs(m - 1, j, board);         }         for(int i = 0; i < m; i++) {             for(int j = 0; j < n; j++) {                 if(board[i][j] == '*')                     board[i][j] = 'O';                 else if(board[i][j] == 'O')                     board[i][j] = 'X';             }         }     }     void dfs(int row, int col, vector<vector<char>>& board) {         if(board[row][col] != 'O') return;         board[row][col] = '*';         if(row - 1 > 0) dfs(row - 1, col, board);         if(col - 1 > 0) dfs(row, col - 1, board);         if(row + 1 < m) dfs(row + 1, col, board);         if(col + 1 < n) dfs(row, col + 1, board);     } };
